    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : MR. D. M. [REDACTED] 137 67C",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: December 28, 1948",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM : [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Reference is made to the teletype of December 28, 1948,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "from the Houston Office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "At 3:30 p.m., I called SAC Hood of the Los Angeles Office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "and instructed that he attempt to locate Mr. [REDACTED] and Mr. and Mrs.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] secure photographs and film in their possession and also",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "secure from them the location of the described flying disc. I also",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "instructed that Mr. Hood send out sufficient Agents to find the disc",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "and guard it until it could be properly handled by the appropriate Government",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "authority. I also telephoned the Houston Office and told them to send",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "in the photographs or film in their possession, together with the part which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "had been recovered from the machine by the Informant Noack.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "At 5:00 p.m., SAC Hood called back and stated that all work on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "this matter should be immediately discontinued. They had managed to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "reach Mr. [REDACTED] and he stated that he knew all about this matter;",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "that it was not a flying disc, but an object which had been identified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "as a tow kite, which has a disc center and wings. This kite is actually",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "made in Los Angeles by the [REDACTED] Manufacturing Company. A call",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "was made to [REDACTED] who admitted making a kite along the lines",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "described by [REDACTED] and they explained that they had tried to fly it",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "and it had failed and they had abandoned it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Mr. Hood stated he did not have full details at the time of his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "call, but he did have this report from the Agents. Therefore, I instructed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "that he call Mr. [REDACTED] of the Houston Office immediately in order that the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "film and the part available to the Houston Office will not be forwarded",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "for Laboratory examination.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "HBF:esb",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
